                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-92-off564 t18101031-92-cd565"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-92-off566 t18101031-92-cd565"></join>, a tress of hay, value 3 s. a bag, value 1 s. and half a bushel of peas and beans mixed, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18101031-92-victim981" type="victimName">
