                     <interp inst="t18101031-92-off566" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101031-92-off566" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               feloniously receiving, on the same day, a truss of hay, being part and parcel of the above mentioned goods, he knowing them to be stolen
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18101031-92-person984">
                  DANIEL 
                  AUSTIN
               <interp inst="t18101031-92-person984" type="surname" value="AUSTIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101031-92-person984" type="given" value="DANIEL"></interp>
